item.title: Help!
item.dc:creator: @cawagula cawagula
item.description:
@cawagula wrote:

Hey, a few people have had this problem for some reason, and I just helped someone with it eairlier. Here’s the cache folder, I uploaded it myself:

http://rapidshare.de/files/25509539/cache.rar.html

Just unzip and stick in the root MoparScapePriv21 folder. As for the port every server is default unless directed otherwise, so you shouldn’t have to mess with that.
